{"title":"Earrings","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"pyramid-studs","title":"Pyramid studs","description":"\u003cp\u003eGranules form distinct geometric shapes naturally and can be found like these as granulation decoration on antique jewellery throughout different cultures, from the Etruscans to the Assyrians. The pyramid of four spheres is one of them.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs all LURI pieces, these studs are crafted entirely by hand with responsibly sourced \u003ca rel=\"noopener\" href=\"\/asset\/luri.gold\/pages\/about\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ematerials\u003c\/a\u003e. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Schuberthan Gold","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49371599339866,"sku":"","price":300.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC1404.jpg?v=1724678137"},{"product_id":"tourmaline-and-pearl-earrings","title":"Tourmaline and Pearl Earrings","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg\u003e\u003cimg\u003e\u003cimg\u003e\u003cimg\u003eThe colour of these tourmalines changes with the light between a mysterious grey and a celestial blue. Combined with the soft shimmer of white pearls and the warm glow of gold 900 - a festive dream! \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThey can be made with other precious gems and pearls, too. Please \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/pages\/contact\"\u003econtact\u003c\/a\u003e me, together we will create your personal favourite combination. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LURI jewels","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49892115710298,"sku":"","price":1050.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC1906.jpg?v=1731423344"},{"product_id":"chain-earrings-with-imperial-topaz","title":"Chain Earrings with Imperial Topaz","description":"\u003cp\u003eDangling on a handwoven Roman loop-in-loop chain, these drops of golden topaz reflect the light in a subtle way. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWould you like to choose your own favourite gems for a custom design? Please \u003c\/span\u003e\u003ca rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/pages\/contact\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econtact\u003c\/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e me, together we will find the perfect fit. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LURI jewels","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49905477976410,"sku":"","price":1000.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC1304.jpg?v=1731585956"},{"product_id":"granulated-studs","title":"Granulated Studs","description":"\u003cp\u003eA rising sun for your ear stack, these studs are handmade in gold 900. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Schuberthan Gold","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49909073477978,"sku":"","price":300.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC1399.jpg?v=1731600231"},{"product_id":"granulated-emerald-studs","title":"Granulated Emerald Studs","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe intense green of these Brazilian emeralds is a perfect combination with the warm colour of the gold 900. Emerald is the birthstone of May and the inclusions in the gems are called \u003cem\u003ejardin\u003c\/em\u003e - garden, reminding of the green leaves that spring brings back. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe studs are available also with your personal favourite gem, please \u003ca rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/pages\/contact\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econtact\u003c\/a\u003e me for any customisation. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LURI jewels","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50466257142106,"sku":"","price":350.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2252_cdb04633-be32-4caf-b798-45308d9b7124.jpg?v=1739553191"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/collections\/DSC1906.jpg?v=1731603741","url":"https:\/\/luri.gold\/collections\/earrings.oembed","provider":"LURI jewels","version":"1.0","type":"link"}